videos.description: Trent Forrest picks off the pass and gives to Devin Vassell for a Florida State dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Forrest's steal leads to a Vassell dunk) 2020/2/8

videos.headline: Forrest's steal leads to a Vassell dunk

videos.description: Miami tries to maintain possession, but they lose the ball, and it ends up with Devin Vassell, who finishes with a score for Florida State.
videos.headline: Vassell scores off Miami turnover

videos.description: Florida State is able to break Miami's defense and gets the ball to Patrick Williams for a dunk. A little later, Williams misses after grabbing a rebound, but he cashes in with another rebound and another dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams slams a pair of dunks) 2020/2/8

videos.headline: Williams slams a pair of dunks
